er 230 unique items to collect, you can craft new items, upgrade your base, and trade with merchants.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/4d59ee64e36a153a48d6eb841efed193.poster.avif?t=1740152000\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/4d59ee64e36a153a48d6eb841efed193.webm?t=1740152000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641490/extras/4d59ee64e36a153a48d6eb841efed193.mp4?t=1740152000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock Skills & Upgrade Your Base</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up to unlock skill points, which can be spent on levelling up skills, giving you a distinct edge in the wasteland. Craft new building units and decorations to make your base unique to you. Level up building units to unlock crafting recipes, repairing, permanent perks, and storage space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
